# --- VaultOS template .gitignore ---
# Standard: git tracks only what Obsidian Sync does not carry. Obsidian config is
# Sync-owned — EXCEPT the CSS snippets, which the wiki rendering (infobox /
# home-grid / figures) depends on. A fresh clone has no shared Sync, so the
# snippets must travel with the template.
.obsidian/*
!.obsidian/snippets/

# Web Clipper drop zone — raw clips stay local until triage routes them into raw/
inbox/Clippings/
Inbox/Clippings/

# Bulky binary / raw exports stay local-cold unless deliberately promoted
raw/**/*.pdf
raw/**/*.zip
raw/**/*.png
raw/**/*.jpg
raw/**/*.jpeg
raw/**/*.json
raw/**/*.csv

# Machine-local Claude Code settings
.claude/settings.local.json

# Non-Claude agent skill mirror — generated per-vault from .claude/skills by the
# mirror hook; the template ships AGENTS.md (the pointer), not a static mirror.
.agents/

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*~
*.swp
